        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '\"Death\"', 3: 'Just part of a trade? Do you have any clue what\\'s gone down in the mortal realm since the Hell Train bit the dust? Bloodsworn, tell her what you\\'ve seen with your own eyes!', 4: '1'}"
